data.description: Beautifull home.  Close to Park and Pool. Huge Master Bedroom (19x14) w/Master Bath (16x7). Whirlpool Tub & Separate Shower. Wood Laminate Floors (Family Room & Stairs), Tile Floors (KIT/BRK/Utility/Bathrooms) & Carpet (Bedrooms/Halls). Large Oak Tree in Backyard Covering an Elevated Wood Deck. Game Room Plus Study! For the Area, You Won't Beat the Price or Square Footage Offered! The Perfect Family Home!
